First of all, we don't all track each other's personality so closely. I 
have no idea whether Mac is "fussily meticulous". 

Secondly, and more importantly, saying Saga would have sent the letter 
does not cast aspersions at Mac. Lots of things could have gone wrong. We 
know she was moving house. Perhaps it got sent to the old address and 
wasn't forwarded correctly. Perhaps it got sent to the new address, and 
got wrongly forwarded to the previous occupant's new address. Perhaps it 
got sent during the postal strike and a temporary postal worker lost it.

